we get the hell out of here. okay?

784
00:46:31.247 --> 00:46:32.457
- Me too.
- (ALARM BLARES)

785
00:46:34.542 --> 00:46:36.794
- Did you get any of that shit on you?
- No.

786
00:46:36.878 --> 00:46:37.879
(STRAINING) You sure?

787
00:46:37.962 --> 00:46:39.631
- No.
- (GRUNTS) Great.

788
00:46:41.591 --> 00:46:43.343
