You can clear the line now.

813
00:48:28.489 --> 00:48:29.490
Yes. sir.

814
00:48:29.574 --> 00:48:31.075
Hello. Robert.

815
00:48:31.159 --> 00:48:32.201
How's the back?

816
00:48:32.285 --> 00:48:34.120
