to bed 20 years ago.

818
00:48:37.332 --> 00:48:40.001
<i>Eighteen. Apparently. it woke up.</i>

819
00:48:40.084 --> 00:48:43.713
- Sounds like a broken thermistor to me.
- That would be nice to think.

820
00:48:44.297 --> 00:48:47.467
